<paragraph id="F45436C1FFEEFFB6FD89FD85AC4EFD74" blockId="8.[136,1452,158,689]" pageId="8" pageNumber="100">
<emphasis id="C69FEAD3FFEEFFB6FD89FD85AC04FDE5" bold="true" box="[189,357,518,544]" pageId="8" pageNumber="100">Observations:</emphasis>
<bibRefCitation id="907A4B30FFEEFFB6FC59FD85AF15FDE5" author="Villalobos, N. &amp; Finot, V. &amp; Ruiz, E. &amp; Penailillo, P. &amp; Collado, G." box="[365,628,518,545]" pageId="8" pageNumber="100" pagination="93 - 136" refId="ref11988" refString="Villalobos, N., Finot, V., Ruiz, E., Penailillo, P. &amp; Collado, G. (2019) Estudio morfometrico y taxonomico de las especies nativas chilenas del genero Anthoxanthum (Poaceae, Pooideae, Poeae, Anthoxanthinae). Darwiniana, Nueva Serie 7: 93 - 136. https: // doi. org / 10.14522 / darwiniana. 2019.71.822" type="journal article" year="2019">
Villalobos 
<emphasis id="C69FEAD3FFEEFFB6FCDCFD84AF7BFDE5" box="[488,538,518,544]" italics="true" pageId="8" pageNumber="100">et al</emphasis>
. (2019)
</bibRefCitation>
indicated that this taxon should be kept as a species based on the digital image of the 
<typeStatus id="2B508863FFEEFFB6FC22FDA8AC27FD80" box="[278,326,555,581]" pageId="8" pageNumber="100">type</typeStatus>
and on previous descriptions by 
<bibRefCitation id="907A4B30FFEEFFB6FF99FDA9AE27FD81" author="Parodi, L. R." box="[685,838,554,580]" pageId="8" pageNumber="100" pagination="183 - 212" refId="ref10950" refString="Parodi, L. R. (1941) Revision de las gramineas sudamericanas del genero Hierochloe. Revista del Museo de La Plata (N. S.) 3 (14): 183 - 212." type="journal article" year="1941">Parodi (1941)</bibRefCitation>
and 
<bibRefCitation id="907A4B30FFEEFFB6FE4DFDA8A951FD80" author="De Paula, M. E." box="[889,1072,554,581]" pageId="8" pageNumber="100" pagination="422 - 457" refId="ref10151" refString="De Paula, M. E. (1975) Las especies del genero Hierochloe (Gramineae) de Argentina y Chile. Darwiniana 19: 422 - 457." type="journal article" year="1975">De Paula (1975)</bibRefCitation>
. However, according to Villalobos 
<emphasis id="C69FEAD3FFEEFFB6FDBCFDCCADD8FDAD" box="[136,185,590,616]" italics="true" pageId="8" pageNumber="100">et al</emphasis>
. (l.c.), all the specimens assigned to this taxon by 
<bibRefCitation id="907A4B30FFEEFFB6FFDFFDCCAEC3FDAC" author="De Paula, M. E." box="[747,930,590,617]" pageId="8" pageNumber="100" pagination="422 - 457" refId="ref10151" refString="De Paula, M. E. (1975) Las especies del genero Hierochloe (Gramineae) de Argentina y Chile. Darwiniana 19: 422 - 457." type="journal article" year="1975">De Paula (1975)</bibRefCitation>
correspond to 
<taxonomicName id="33EB4D42FFEEFFB6F97CFDCCA9B0FDAD" box="[1096,1233,590,616]" class="Liliopsida" family="Poaceae" genus="Anthoxanthum" kingdom="Plantae" order="Poales" pageId="8" pageNumber="100" phylum="Tracheophyta" rank="species" species="gunckelii">
<emphasis id="C69FEAD3FFEEFFB6F97CFDCCA9B0FDAD" box="[1096,1233,590,616]" italics="true" pageId="8" pageNumber="100">H. gunckelii</emphasis>
</taxonomicName>
. In addition to this, molecular analyses by 
<bibRefCitation id="907A4B30FFEEFFB6FCBDFDF1AFD1FD49" author="Lema-Suarez, I. &amp; Sahuquillo, E. &amp; Estevez, G. &amp; Loureiro, J. &amp; Castro, S. &amp; Pimentel, M." box="[393,688,626,653]" pageId="8" pageNumber="100" pagination="389 - 413" refId="ref10670" refString="Lema-Suarez, I., Sahuquillo, E., Estevez, G., Loureiro, J., Castro, S. &amp; Pimentel, M. (2018) A taxonomic and evolutionary review of the South American Hierochloe sect. Monoecia Connor (Poaceae; Anthoxanthinae). Botanical Journal of the Linnean Society 186: 389 - 413. https: // doi. org / 10.1093 / botlinnean / box 102" type="journal article" year="2018">
Lema-Suárez 
<emphasis id="C69FEAD3FFEEFFB6FF11FDF0AF36FD49" box="[549,599,626,652]" italics="true" pageId="8" pageNumber="100">et al</emphasis>
. (2018)
</bibRefCitation>
placed 
<taxonomicName id="33EB4D42FFEEFFB6FE33FDF0AE1AFD49" authorityName="Parodi" authorityYear="1941" box="[775,891,627,652]" class="Liliopsida" family="Poaceae" genus="Hierochloe" higherTaxonomySource="GBIF" kingdom="Plantae" order="Poales" pageId="8" pageNumber="100" phylum="Tracheophyta" rank="species" species="spicata">
<emphasis id="C69FEAD3FFEEFFB6FE33FDF0AE1AFD49" box="[775,891,627,652]" italics="true" pageId="8" pageNumber="100">H. spicata</emphasis>
</taxonomicName>
in an unresolved clade with all the other varieties of 
<taxonomicName id="33EB4D42FFEEFFB6FD92FD14AC49FD75" authorityName="Roemer &amp; Schultes" authorityYear="1817" baseAuthorityName="Vahl" baseAuthorityYear="1791" box="[166,296,662,688]" class="Liliopsida" family="Poaceae" genus="Hierochloe" higherTaxonomySource="GBIF" kingdom="Plantae" order="Poales" pageId="8" pageNumber="100" phylum="Tracheophyta" rank="species" species="redolens">
<emphasis id="C69FEAD3FFEEFFB6FD92FD14AC49FD75" box="[166,296,662,688]" italics="true" pageId="8" pageNumber="100">H. redolens</emphasis>
</taxonomicName>
.
</paragraph>
